content: निर्वाहः {@--1@} Carrying on, accomplishng, performing. {@--2@} Completion, end. {@--3@} Carrying to the end, supporting, steadfast adherence, perseverance; निर्वाहः प्रतिपन्नवस्तुषु सतामेतद्धि गोत्रव्रतं <ls>Mu. 2. 18.</ls> {@--4@} Subsisting on. {@--5@} Sufficiency, competent provision, competency. {@--6@} Describing, narrating.
